# Volunteer-management-app
Creation of a web app that will help manage and optimize their volunteer activities. it will include the following: Volunteer’s location, Volunteer’s skills and preferences, Volunteer’s availability, Event requirements and location, Task urgency and priority. 

Tasks to accomplish:
1) create a login/register page: planned use of HTML and CCS
2) After registration redirct to log in and create their profile which must include: location, skills, preferences, and availability
3) allow event management to create and manage(edit) events and need to include: specifying required skills, location, and urgency
4) after user and management registration/creation of events, match the volunteers to events/tasks by comparing their profiles.
5) Notify the user and management when there is a match
6) create a page that stores the history of what the volunteer has done in the past.



